OL,3,CFoster mother of baby felt something
OL,4,Cwas wrong, murder trial hears
OL,6,FA foster mother had a "gut feeling"
OL,7,Fsomething was wrong before a boy was
OL,8,Fallegedly sexually abused and murdered
OL,9,Fby his adopted parents, a court has
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FSandra Cooper looked after Preston
OL,13,FDavey after his birth in June 2022,
OL,14,Fwhen he was taken into care by Oldham
OL,15,FCouncil, aged just five days old, a
OL,16,Fjury at Preston Crown Court heard.
OL,26,@nD@WOUnD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
