OL,3,CFoster mother of baby felt something
OL,4,Cwas wrong, murder trial hears
OL,6,FMrs Cooper and husband Paul fostered
OL,7,FPreston until he was 10-months-old,
OL,8,Fwhen in April 2023 he was given up for
OL,9,Fadoption to high school teacher Jamie
OL,10,FVarley, 37, and his partner John
OL,11,FMcGowan-Fazakerley, 32.
OL,13,FMrs Cooper said of the youngster: "He
OL,14,Fwas beautiful, he was happy, he
OL,15,Flaughed, he smiled really early. Just
OL,16,Fa really lovable baby. He loved
OL,17,Fcuddles. He was just having a really
OL,18,Fnice life.
OL,26,@uD@cOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
