PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776885106
OL,3,CFoster mother of baby felt something
OL,4,Cwas wrong, murder trial hears
OL,6,F"He was a baby who took part, he would
OL,7,Fbe interacting, smiling at you. That's
OL,8,Fwho he was."
OL,10,FIn just under the next four months
OL,11,Fafter his adoption at the defendants'
OL,12,Fhome in Blackpool, he was allegedly
OL,13,Froutinely ill-treated, had indecent
OL,14,Fimages and videos taken of him,
OL,15,Fsexually abused and physically
OL,16,Fassaulted, suffering 40 traumatic
OL,17,Finjuries.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
