PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776885106
OL,3,CFoster mother of baby felt something
OL,4,Cwas wrong, murder trial hears
OL,6,FHe died in hospital on 27 July 2023
OL,7,Fhaving suffered a collapse and cardiac
OL,8,Farrest allegedly following a sexual
OL,9,Fassault by Varley.
OL,11,FVarley is accused of murder and 25
OL,12,Fother charges relating to his sexual
OL,13,Fand physical mistreatment of the child.
OL,15,FMcGowan-Fazakerley is accused of
OL,16,Fallowing the death of a child and four
OL,17,Fother charges relating to abuse or
OL,18,Fmistreatment of the child.
OL,20,FBoth men deny all charges.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
