PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776885106
OL,3,CFoster mother of baby felt something
OL,4,Cwas wrong, murder trial hears
OL,6,FMrs Cooper, who had fostered 43
OL,7,Fchildren over 27 years, said there was
OL,8,Fa gradual familiarisation with the
OL,9,Fadoptive parents before finally giving
OL,10,FPreston up for adoption and the child
OL,11,Fmoving into the defendants' home on 3
OL,12,FApril 2023.
OL,14,FBut, afterwards, planned visits by her
OL,15,Fto see the child had been made
OL,16,Fdifficult by the defendants, she
OL,17,Fclaimed.
OL,19,FMrs Cooper said she had difficulty
OL,20,Fgetting access to see Preston and made
OL,21,Fa complaint to a social worker.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
