PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776885106
OL,3,CFoster mother of baby felt something
OL,4,Cwas wrong, murder trial hears
OL,6,FShe told the jury: "I was worried. I
OL,7,Ffelt like something is wrong. I felt
OL,8,Flike they were hiding him from me.
OL,10,F"It's just my, call it gut feeling. I
OL,11,Ffelt like something was wrong."
OL,13,FEventually a date was made and she got
OL,14,Fto see Preston for the last time.
OL,16,F"It was made difficult for us but I
OL,17,Fwould've walked to the ends of the
OL,18,Fearth for that visit," Mrs Cooper said.
OL,26,@nD@TOUrD@AOUsD@_O]xD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
