PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776885106
OL,3,CFoster mother of baby felt something
OL,4,Cwas wrong, murder trial hears
OL,6,F"He just looked a bit stiff, a bit
OL,7,Fblank, but we had not seen him for a
OL,8,Fwhile. I was just really glad to see
OL,9,Fhim."
OL,11,FAmy Shepherdson, Preston's social
OL,12,Fworker with Oldham Borough Council,
OL,13,Fwas part of a team to find prospective
OL,14,Fadoptive parents and made home visits
OL,15,Fafter the adoption.
OL,17,FThe social worker was asked about the
OL,18,Fthree times Preston was taken to
OL,19,Fhospital in the just under four months
OL,20,Fhe was with the defendants before his
OL,21,Fdeath.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
