PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776885106
OL,3,CFoster mother of baby felt something
OL,4,Cwas wrong, murder trial hears
OL,6,FMs Shepherdson said on 25 May 2023,
OL,7,Fshe was sent a Whatsapp message from
OL,8,FVarley to say Preston was in hospital,
OL,9,Fdiagnosed with a chest infection and
OL,10,Fwas undergoing scans.
OL,12,FShe said the hospital admission of a
OL,13,F"looked after" child had raised a
OL,14,Fsafeguarding issue and police officers
OL,15,Fvisited the ward, but a medical
OL,16,Fexplanation had been provided for the
OL,17,Fbaby's visit and this assuaged any
OL,18,Fconcerns.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776885106
OL,3,CFoster mother of baby felt something
OL,4,Cwas wrong, murder trial hears
OL,6,FOn 30 June, Preston was taken to
OL,7,Fhospital again with a "fever" and the
OL,8,Fsocial worker conducted a home visit
OL,9,Fon 4 July, where Ms Shepherdson noted
OL,10,Fthe child was "pale and did not seem
OL,11,Fhimself. Very little energy", adding
OL,12,Fhe was a little boy "that had been
OL,13,Fpoorly".
OL,15,FOn 10 July, Preston was again in
OL,16,Fhospital after a fracture to his left
OL,17,Felbow.
OL,19,FVarley had made a video call to the
OL,20,Fsocial worker, explaining what
OL,21,Fhappened, she said.
OL,26,@oD@WOUoD@]O]rD@OOUsD@\O]tD@UOUuD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
