PN,39110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776885106
OL,3,CFoster mother of baby felt something
OL,4,Cwas wrong, murder trial hears
OL,6,FMs Shepherdson said: "Jamie looked
OL,7,Fgrey, he was beside himself, he was
OL,8,Fteary. He said Preston looked in pain.
OL,9,FHe had unintentionally hurt Preston."
OL,11,FShe said Varley told her the child had
OL,12,Fwoken in the night, he had gone to
OL,13,Fsettle the baby and when putting him
OL,14,Fback down in his cot, Preston had
OL,15,Ftwisted and "he heard a sound like a
OL,16,Fknee clicking".
OL,26,@nD@VOUqD@eO]wD@MOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
