PN,39111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776885106
OL,3,CFoster mother of baby felt something
OL,4,Cwas wrong, murder trial hears
OL,6,FMs Shepherdson said after contacting
OL,7,Fthe hospital and speaking to the ward
OL,8,Fsister, she was told there were no
OL,9,Fsafeguarding worries and she visited
OL,10,FPreston's home that day.
OL,12,FPreston appeared his usual, playful
OL,13,Fself, Ms Shepherdson said, adding: "I
OL,14,Fdid not have any concerns."
OL,16,FMs Shepherdson told the court her next
OL,17,Finvolvement was on July 27, 2023.
OL,19,F"I got a phone call from John to
OL,20,Fadvise that Preston had died," she
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,26,@uD@dOUvD@[O]{D@AOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
