PN,39112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776885106
OL,3,CFoster mother of baby felt something
OL,4,Cwas wrong, murder trial hears
OL,6,FPreston had been rushed into hospital
OL,7,Funconscious and in a state of cardiac
OL,8,Farrest, and medics could not revive
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,FVarley told police the child had
OL,12,Fdrowned while left in the bath.
OL,14,FA Home Office post-mortem examination
OL,15,Ffound multiple non-accidental,
OL,16,Finternal and external injuries, and a
OL,17,Fcause of death to be acute upper
OL,18,Fairways obstruction by either
OL,19,Fsmothering or an object or objects
OL,20,Finserted into his mouth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
